Subject: [PATCH v4 2/7] sched/preempt: refactor sched_dynamic_update()
Date:   Mon, 14 Feb 2022 16:52:11 +0000
Message-Id: <20220214165216.2231574-3-mark.rutland@arm.com>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.30.2
In-Reply-To: <20220214165216.2231574-1-mark.rutland@arm.com>
